the first writer to receive the nobel prize for literature ( given " in special recognition of his poetic composition , which gives evidence of lofty idealism , artistic perfection and a rare combination of the qualities of both heart and intellect " ) , he devoted the bulk of the money he received to the creation of a poetry prize awarded by the société des gens de lettres .

